Given this cipher spec and metrics, propose an ImprovementPatch.
CipherSpec JSON:
{
  "name": "SPN_Weak_46",
  "architecture": "SPN",
  "block_size_bits": 128,
  "key_size_bits": 128,
  "rounds": 8,
  "components": {
    "sbox": "sbox.identity",
    "perm": "perm.identity",
    "linear": "linear.identity",
    "key_schedule": "ks.sha256_kdf"
  },
  "version": "0.1",
  "notes": "",
  "seed": 1337
}
Metrics JSON:
{
  "plaintext_avalanche": {
    "mean": 0.22
  },
  "key_avalanche": {
    "mean": 0.28
  }
}

{
  "summary": "Increase diffusion and nonlinearity to improve avalanche.",
  "rationale": [
    "Identity S-box/linear layer provide almost no confusion/diffusion.",
    "More rounds and standard AES-like components generally improve avalanche in SPN prototypes."
  ],
  "new_rounds": 12,
  "replace_components": {
    "sbox": "sbox.aes",
    "perm": "perm.aes_shiftrows",
    "linear": "linear.aes_mixcolumns"
  },
  "add_notes": "This patch is a hypothesis aimed at improving avalanche; it is not a proof of security."
}

Given this cipher spec and metrics, propose an ImprovementPatch.
CipherSpec JSON:
{
  "name": "FEISTEL_Weak_25",
  "architecture": "FEISTEL",
  "block_size_bits": 64,
  "key_size_bits": 128,
  "rounds": 12,
  "components": {
    "f_sbox": "sbox.identity",
    "f_perm": "perm.identity",
    "key_schedule": "ks.sha256_kdf"
  },
  "version": "0.1",
  "notes": "",
  "seed": 2026
}
Metrics JSON:
{
  "plaintext_avalanche": {
    "mean": 0.3
  },
  "key_avalanche": {
    "mean": 0.31
  }
}

{
  "summary": "Strengthen the Feistel round function and add rounds to improve diffusion.",
  "rationale": [
    "Feistel invertibility does not require an invertible F, but identity F-like behavior reduces confusion.",
    "Adding a nonlinear S-box and additional rounds tends to increase avalanche in toy constructions."
  ],
  "new_rounds": 16,
  "replace_components": {
    "f_sbox": "sbox.aes"
  },
  "add_notes": "If avalanche remains low after this change, consider increasing rounds further or altering key mixing."
}
